    Constructor
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>RenderPluginEnumerator</TypeRef> constructor creates a renderer plugin enumerator using the supplied logger for plugin loading diagnostics.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[explicit RenderPluginEnumerator(cobalt::logging::ILogger::unique_ptr log);]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Argument list">
      <ArgumentList>
        <ArgumentListEntry Type="cobalt::logging::ILogger::unique_ptr" Name="log">
          The logger transferred to the plugin enumerator.
        </ArgumentListEntry>
      </ArgumentList>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
